----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Attribution
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
The human-attention data under `priors/` and `dataset_sample/` was derived
from eye-tracking studies reported in Zhang et al., 2024, "EyeTrans: Merging
Human and Machine Attention for Neural Code Summarization" (FSE'24). When
using these files in research, please cite both that paper and the EyeMulator
paper (see CITATION.bib).
